这是手脚的：/execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..4] run data merge entity @s {NoBasePlate:1}让周围的盔甲架没有底盘
/execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..4] run data merge entity @s {ShowArms:1}让周围的盔甲架加手

这个是动作的：/execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..10] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{RightArm:[0.0f,0.0f,100.0f]}}

这里要解释的就是在RightArm（这个大家都懂）后面的三个数字，就是三个f前面的0），第一个的它手臂摆动的前后角度，可以是正数也可以是负数，那个 f 必须要的;第二个是手臂旋转的角度，第三个是手臂抬起来的高度。以此类推：

调整左脚角度 /execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..4] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{LeftLeg:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

调整头角度 /execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..5] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{Head:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

调整左手角度 /execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..4] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{LeftArm:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

调整右脚角度 　/execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..5] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{RightLeg:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

调整右手角度 /execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..4] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{RightArm:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

调整身体角度 　/execute as @e[type=minecraft:armor_stand,distance=..5] run data merge entity @s {Pose:{Body:[0.0f,0.0f,0.0f]}}

这是手脚的：/entitydata @e[type=ArmorStand,r=4] {NoBasePlate:1}让周围的盔甲架没有底盘

/entitydata @e[type=ArmorStand,r=4] {ShowArms:1}让周围的盔甲架加手

这个是动作的：/entitydata @e[type=ArmorStand,r=10] {Pose:{RightArm:[0f,0f,100f]}}
我忘记这个适用于1.8还是1.13之后的指令了  大概就是这个
